title: The Apple Studio Display Is WEIRD!
description:
Apple's new Studio Display has been both praised and panned—as usual, we feel things are a bit more nuanced and many reviewers have missed the mark. Is it good? Yes. Is it expensive? Certainly. Most of all, though? It's just downright weird.
